  "title": "All-Party Parliamentary Group for Young Carers and Young Adult Carers",
  "purpose": "A forum for key issues affecting young carers and young adult carers, championing their involvement and voice, to be addressed collaboratively by parliamentarians. To encourage improved support, services and recognition. Other key stakeholders such as the public and third sectors will also be brought together.",
